                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8169" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1271</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2094 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">统借统还业务中借款主体企业F公司的合同风险管控</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Contract Risk Control of the Borrowing Entity-F company in the Unified Borrowing and Repayment Business</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马成慧，杨霞，李艳，康萍，胡鹏，孙成真，周琳，周明彤，徐绍波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南先锋煤业开发有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贷款转借；合同风险；合同执行；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">loan subordination; contract risk; contract implementation    </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">F公司是Q集团的子公司，出于集团资金平衡的需要，F公司作为借款主体分别向两家银行进行借款，再以同等条件转借给Q集团使用，由Q集团及Q集团的母公司为此进行担保。借款到期后，Q集团未能按约定偿付欠款。对此，借款主体F公司多次与银行办理展期。最终由Q集团母公司对这笔借款进行清偿。之后，F公司多次向Q集团申请贷款转借合同对应展期、债权抵销部分债权或三方债权债务抵消，均没有得到Q集团的回应。直到Q集团内部司法重整时才偿还了借款合同本息并承担了高昂的罚息和滞纳金。借款主体F公司的损失得以降至最低。企业集团进行统借统还，作为借款主体企业，必然面临合同风险、利息风险、票据风险等威胁，本案例对F公司所面临的合同风险，以及如何规避进行讨论，引导学生思考内部控制及风险管理的重要性，以及贯彻执行相关的制度对企业风险管理的意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> F company is a subsidiary of Q Group. For the Group’s capital balancing needs, F company got loans from two banks and then sub-lent the loans to Q under same conditions. The loans were guaranteed by Q and its parent company. Q Group failed to repay as agreed when the loan matured. F Company had to negotiate loan extension with banks several times. The loans were repaid by the parent company of Q Group eventually. Afterwards，F Company repeatedly applied for the loan transfer contract from Q Group to settle the loan extension, or offset the debt partially with other debts or offset the loans by another debt between F company and third party. All the proposals are neglected by Q Group. Until the internal judicial settlement of Q group, the principal and interest were repaid with hefty overdue fine and interest penalties. F company’s loss was minimized. In the unified borrowing and repayment, the borrowing entity is inevitably under threat of contract risk, interest risk, bill risk, etc. This case discusses the contract risk and risk-aversion of F company. With the purpose of guiding students to consider the importance of internal control and risk management, as well as the significance of implementing relevant systems for enterprise risk management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》、《高级会计实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业风险管理；内部控制系统；控制环境；控制活动</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
